metadata.name: ToadzBogz
metadata.description:
Went to the swamp to get the scoop. CrypToadz out there ganged-up in a troop.

For updates on this road map of this collection, please follow https://twitter.com/zamees.

This idea began by wanting to teach myself Illustrator, so I started asking Cryptoadz owners if they'd like their toadz "zameesified." As I got into the intricacies of the art, I also began developing a style...and it just keeps !vibing.

52 toadz were used in this piece (11 of them newly created in The Zamees Labz) with some halves and pieces on the edges.

This is the first piece: toadz in LIFE > strife > dead > resurrected.

These pieces may (or may not) be relevant later...
